Boris Johnson got the government’s self-isolation support payment wrong on Sky News.

People who have to isolate are entitled to £500 in total, not £500 per week.

Partnerships with internet platforms are vital for fact checkers who want to tackle misinformation on the same scale as it is being produced.

By working together, we can create better models for distributing fact checks online.
